.TH "update_sg_lb_stats" 9 "update_sg_lb_stats" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
update_sg_lb_stats \- Update sched_group's statistics for load balancing.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" update_sg_lb_stats
.BI "(struct lb_env *env "  ","
.BI "struct sched_group *group "  ","
.BI "struct sg_lb_stats *sgs "  ","
.BI "int *sg_status "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "env" 12
The load balancing environment.
.IP "group" 12
sched_group whose statistics are to be updated.
.IP "sgs" 12
variable to hold the statistics for this group.
.IP "sg_status" 12
Holds flag indicating the status of the sched_group
